                    <h3>How do I initiate a return?</h3>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Follow these simple steps:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Log into your account and go to 'My Orders'</li>
                        <li>Select the item you wish to return</li>
                        <li>Choose a return reason (size, color, etc.)</li>
                        <li>Print the return label provided</li>
                        <li>Package the item securely with original tags</li>
                        <li>Drop off at the nearest pickup location or schedule a pickup</li>
