                    <h3>What if I receive a damaged or defective item?</h3>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience. Please:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Contact us within 48 hours of delivery</li>
                        <li>Send photos of the damaged/defective area</li>
                        <li>Include your order number and details</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We'll arrange a free pickup and replacement immediately. For manufacturing defects, we offer:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Free replacement of the same item</li>
                        <li>Exchange for any other product</li>
                        <li>Full refund if preferred</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-card">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>Do you offer exchanges?</h3>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! We offer easy exchanges for:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Size exchanges:</strong> Within 15 days for a different size</li>
                        <li><strong>Color exchanges:</strong> If available in stock</li>
                        <li><strong>Style exchanges:</strong> For equal or higher value items</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Exchange Process:</strong></p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Initiate exchange through 'My Orders'</li>
                        <li>Choose your preferred size/color</li>
                        <li>We'll ship the new item once we receive your return</li>
                        <li>No additional shipping charges for exchanges within India</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
