                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We recommend following these steps:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Measure yourself:</strong> Use a soft measuring tape</li>
                        <li><strong>Key measurements:</strong> Bust, waist, hips, and length</li>
                        <li><strong>Compare:</strong> Check against our size chart for each product</li>
                        <li><strong>Consider style:</strong> Different styles fit differently</li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="size-tip">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        <p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> If between sizes, we recommend sizing up for comfort.</p>
